Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.19,1:22:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,not what it is here. And it's not where\Nit'll be 10 years from now. That's part
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.60,1:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of being complete is having what you\Nneed, uh what you'd like, etc. Go from
