Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.00,1:24:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the presence of God within you,\Nyou wouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.48,1:24:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,\Nthis owes its existence to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.00,1:24:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And humility is when this self begins to\Nacknowledge that it's this is its
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.56,1:24:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,source. This is its source. the infant\Nitself with no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.28,1:24:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I fell into that state\Nin a snowbank once
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.60,1:24:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in uh Wisconsin a million miles from\Nnowhere in a storm and I shoveled the
