Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.92,1:24:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning and no end\Nwas no different than that which I am
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.23,1:24:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am always existed. existed\Nwill always exist. It has no beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.71,1:25:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and no end. And then I be new realized\Nthat I was eternal and that love was
