Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.04,1:25:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own without a single thought.\NWithout a single thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.96,1:25:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And also in that state\Nyou have permission to leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.44,1:25:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've had every time that's recurred\NI've had permission to leave the world
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.40,1:25:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,goes with it. There is nothing no reason\Nfurther to continue in a physical
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.28,1:25:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,existence. So you can leave if you wish\Nyou have complete permission to expire.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.76,1:25:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Each time there was something that\NI was uh for the sake of the love of
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.36,1:25:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,someone uh I declined the offer but it's\Nrecurred over and over. uh you have
