Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.15,1:26:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness,\Nthings that can only be learned within
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.60,1:26:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the limited\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.60,1:26:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,uh\Nwithin the limited domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.28,1:27:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The word I want for it is\Nhello.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.28,1:27:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NAccept the limitations of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.56,1:27:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be a human. It's okay to be\Nhuman. And the limitations of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.60,1:27:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be human.\NWhat is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.92,1:27:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Don't pay any attention to the wizard.\N>> What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.84,1:27:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,\N>> don't pay any attention to the man
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.32,1:27:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,behind the screen.\NHappiness is an intention. It's an
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.04,1:28:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,intention that you wish to be happy and\Nnot make it a dependent on happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.08,1:28:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy if I get that car. I'll be\Nhappy if I get that promotion. I'll be
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.32,1:28:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy if I get uh fried egg sandwich.\NHappiness is a an overall intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.71,1:28:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to be get there is reflection\Nversus impulsivity.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.60,1:28:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation is a wonderful uh spiritual\Ntechnique
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.76,1:28:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's limited. is limited. You can't\Ndrive your car and also be in a
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.23,1:28:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,meditative state.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.12,1:28:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,being reflective,\Nreflect, reflect versus impulsive. So
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.48,1:28:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,when you as you move through the world\Nand make decisions,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.96,1:28:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you become increasingly reflective of\Nall the nuances and the implications
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.96,1:29:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the overall spiritual context.\Nthoughtful rather than critical.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.04,1:29:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always find something to\Ncriticize. You can always find something
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.88,1:29:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to criticize. I had a good time\Ncriticizing the snowoon,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.67,1:29:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,criticizing the wind. I think, geez,\Nthis place is windy. My god, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.76,1:29:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,blowing my head off. It's\Ncritical of the weather. I figure that's
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.19,1:29:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a good thing for a human being to do.\NComplain about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.08,1:29:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot, it's too cold, it's too windy,\Nit's too breezy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.36,1:29:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can enjoy the downside of being a\Nhuman and then realize it's not really a
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.15,1:29:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,downside.\NAny good human should complain about
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.52,1:29:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,wind blowing your hat off all the time.\NStand up for being a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.44,1:29:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come here to complain.\NBrave, courageous, and honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.67,1:30:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to complain about the weather.\Nhere to complain about taxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.15,1:30:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a protest group for something.\NReflective rather than impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.44,1:30:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughtful rather than critical.\NBe content instead of complaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.84,1:30:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I say be content with complaining.\NWhy shouldn't I be complaining?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.04,1:30:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,be content.\NI'm going to cross out instead of
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.32,1:30:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and put with complaining.\NAny human worth of salt is going to
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.23,1:30:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,complain. Tell it doesn't complain.\NIsn't worth the bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.19,1:30:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you care about life, you'll complain\Nabout it. One reason for complaining is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.28,1:30:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is because you care about life. If you\Ndidn't care about life, you wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.08,1:31:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,complain. You wouldn't complain about\Nthe neighborhood if you don't live
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.08,1:31:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there. So, be content instead of\Ncomplaining is a goal. And realize that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.56,1:31:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,life is a learning curve. You're\Nsomeplace on the curve. You're not
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.28,1:31:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect, nor are you completely an\Nidiot. Life is a learning curve.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.23,1:31:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, be willing to accept that you are\Nwhere you are. Move on to the next
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.08,1:31:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before I get angry and have a fit.\NHurry up. Why aren't they moving it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.08,1:31:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with this world?\NAttention, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.52,1:31:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhoh.\NHappiness is a destination and a
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.63,1:31:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,direction.\NReflective versus impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.92,1:31:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughtful rather than critical.\NBe content instead of complaining
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.12,1:32:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize life is a learning curve.\NI thank all of you who quickly prayed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.36,1:32:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the spiritual techniques that\Nwe have used.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.19,1:32:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for help. And you ask yourself,\Ndoes praying do any good? Am I just
