Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.04,1:33:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits all of humanity. Resist. Wow.\NSo praying is not just a uh
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.96,1:33:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,grade school exercise that you do but\Nit's a you know praying actually is an
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.67,1:33:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of what you have become. You\Nhave become gracious. I think that you
