Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.84,1:33:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity and all of its expressions. One\Nof its expressions is creation and part
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.67,1:34:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation is humankind.\NSo pray contemplate affirm God is my
