Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.76,1:34:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and you sing an inner song.\NDon't worry, be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.44,1:34:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing an inner song. Sing an inner song.\NSing an inner song. You hear a child
