Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.96,1:37:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you learn how to hum to yourself\Nwithout making any noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.84,1:37:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still humming.\NEven when I'm talking in the back of my
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.15,1:37:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,mind there, I'm humming.\NFirm. God is my source and my solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.23,1:37:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And sing an inner song.\NAnd when if you're feeling down, this is
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.71,1:37:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what you need. You can put this on your\Nuh mirror where you put yourself
