Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.00,1:38:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and lost your thumb for Christ's sake.\NI'm not even ready to leave this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.00,1:38:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thumb has gone ahead of me.\NI go to heaven, there's the thumb
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.23,1:38:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for me,\Nsaying, "Where have you been? For God's
