Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.76,1:39:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is sad. Poor old thumb. Oh,\Ndarn it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.11,1:39:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can have a temper tantrum.\NTemper tantrum and self-pity are good.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.19,1:39:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Insist on being miserable and gloomy.\NOh well,
