Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.04,1:39:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be happy you go over the speed\Nlimit, they give you a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.76,1:40:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there to be happy about?\NIt's better to be miserable and gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.88,1:40:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody will interfere with you. However,\Nwhen things get bad,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.88,1:40:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,number 75.\NNow, number 75 I do with myself at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.76,1:40:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see very well anymore, so it's\Nharder to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.88,1:40:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I turn the light on in the bathroom\Nand then I look at myself in the mirror
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.04,1:41:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say\N>> well I do that. I tell myself, "Yours is
