Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.63,1:41:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you go,\N"Yours is the saddest story I've ever
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.96,1:41:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,heard."\NOh, whoa, whoa. Poor David.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.28,1:41:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,\Npoor Davyy boy. Oh, you you have a sad
