Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.19,1:41:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ. What more can you\Ncreeping all day? Just creeping up on
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.44,1:42:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you. Creeping.\NI hear you. I heard you creeping.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.36,1:42:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Make faces at yourself in the\Nmirror. That is a very good one. You
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.63,1:42:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,stop taking yourself so seriously.\NYou see all the options that open up to
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.23,1:42:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you and it's a wonderful spiritual\Npractice.
