Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.56,1:42:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The holy church of giggled.\NThe way to God through giggles.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.88,1:42:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In the if you practice all these things,\Nyou'll be grateful for the gift of life.
